window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>24 hours to stop the crime of the century</b> <b>The race against time is about to begin…</b></p> <p><b>THE TOWER OF LONDON…</b></p> <p>Impenetrable. Well protected. Secure. Home to the most valuable jewels on earth. But once a year, when the Queen attends the State Opening of Parliament, the Metropolitan Police must execute the most secret operation in their armory as they transport the Crown Jewels across London.</p> <p><b>SCOTLAND YARD…</b></p> <p>For decades, the elite squad at Scotland Yard have been in charge of the operation. And for decades, it’s run like clockwork.</p> <p><b>THE HEIST…</b></p> <p>But this year, everything is about to change. Because a master criminal has set his sights on pulling off the most outrageous theft in history—and with a man on the inside, the odds are in his favor.</p> <p><b>Unless the team can stop him before it’s too late…</b></p>"; 
